he thin border between rational and irrational is no longer reliable. Severina confirms Rey Rosa’s privileged place in contemporary world literature.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aBooksellers and booksellingvFiction. 0aBookstoresvFiction. 0aThievesvFiction. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aAndrews, Chris, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z97831106725030 cprintz978030019609240uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030020849840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300208498423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300208498/original  a978-3-11-067250-3  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY